%e A396013 .
%e A396013 .
%e A396013 a(8) = 16 as the existing numbers in the Moore neighborhood when a(8) is being placed are 2, 4, 12 and 14, and 16 is the smallest unused number that shares a factor with all of these numbers.
%e A396013 a(13) = 3 as the existing numbers in the Moore neighborhood when a(13) is being placed are 24 and 6, and 3 is the smallest unused number that shares a factor with both of these numbers.
%Y A396013 Cf. A354434 (start at 1), A336946, A064413, A253279, A257112, A257339.
